  <title>Get help when blocked</title>

  <p>You can get help while playing: </p>
  <list>
    <item>
      <p>Hints. A hint will uncover a tile from the board, but will add ten 
         seconds to the time of the game. To ask for choose <guiseq><gui>Game
         </gui><gui>Hint</gui></guiseq>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>"Too many flags" warning. When activated, this option will inform you
         when you set too much flag in the same area.</p>
    </item>
    <item><p>Third step...</p></item>
  </list>

